Set the org's intelligence-refinement prompt — free-text instruction that steers Leadbay's lead recommendations beyond firmographics. Admin-only. Setting this clears any pending clarification and triggers a full intelligence regeneration (web search + high-reasoning). `dry_run:true` returns the call shape without contacting the backend.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} low-level.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} from agent flow — use leadbay_refine_prompt, which polls for follow-up clarifications.

